title: Upgrade Smart contract for market maker borrowers from Liquidity Staking Pool
body: In reference to https://forums.dydx.community/proposal/discussion/2437-drc-smart-contract-upgrade-for-market-maker-borrowers-from-liquidity-staking-pool/, the smart contract should be upgraded to support deposit cancellation and recovery and ensure that market makers can safely make use of the Liquidity Staking Pool.
author: 0xB933AEe47C438f22DE0747D57fc239FE37878Dd1
